summary: An ordinance accepting the condemnation award for certain property in the south one-half of the northeast one-quarter of the southwest one-quarter of the southeast one-quarter, Sec. 19, Twp. 26 North, Range 4 East, W. M. for the Haller Lake Maintenance Headquarters of the Engineering Department under Ordinance 83792, King County Cause No. 480789, and making an appropriation from the City Street Fund therefor.
